 and uncertainties described in our annual report on Form 20-F for the year ended December 31, 2023, filed on March 15, 2024 and our other filings with the SEC. We undertake no obligation to publicly update any forward-looking statement, whether written or oral, that may be made from time to time, whether as a result of new information, future developments or otherwise. Investor Relations Contact Walter FrankIMS Investor Relations203.972.9200wearabledevices@imsinvestorrelations.com \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\n        \"type\": \"Document\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"lc\": 1,\n      \"type\": \"constructor\",\n      \"id\": [\n        \"langchain\",\n        \"schema\",\n        \"document\",\n        \"Document\"\n      ],\n      \"kwargs\": {\n        \"metadata\": {\n          \"source\": \"https://www.stocktitan.net/news/WLDS/wearable-devices-unveils-the-revolutionary-mudra-link-the-first-ai-2nqborjfhrn0.html\",\n          \"title\": \"Wearable Devices Unveils the Revolutionary Mudra LINK: The First AI Neural Interface Wristband for Android and Beyond | WLDS Stock News\",\n          \"description\": \"Discover Mudra LINK: AI-powered neural wristband for Android & XR devices. Precise gesture control, low latency, and adaptable AI. Pre-order the future of intuitive device interaction this September.\",\n          \"language\": \"en\"\n        },\n        \"page_content\": \"\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nWearable Devices Unveils the Revolutionary Mudra LINK: The First AI Neural Interface Wristband for Android and Beyond | WLDS Stock News\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nSTOCK TITAN\\n\\n\\n\\nLogin\\nSign up\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nLo