     \"description\": \"Do you think you know everything about smartphones? Well, 2024 is going to be a breakthrough year for technology. Foldable phones are set to give tough competition to traditional smartphones. Get ready for best smartphones of 2024.\",\n          \"language\": \"en-US\"\n        },\n        \"page_content\": \"\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n  \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n'OnePlus Nord 4', 'Realme GT6' - 8 Best Smartphones Of 2024 - RVCJ Media\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nAbout Us\\nContact Us\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\nThursday, July 18, 2024 \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Marketing Mind\\n Shop \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n     \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nNo Result \\n\\n View All Result \\n \\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nBollywood & TV\\nEntertainment\\nSports\\nTechnology\\nTravel\\nVideos\\nExtras\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n     \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nBollywood & TV\\nEntertainment\\nSports\\nTechnology\\nTravel\\nVideos\\nExtras\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nNo Result \\n\\n View All Result \\n \\n \\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nNo Result \\n\\n View All Result \\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nHome\\n\\nTechnology\\n \\n\\n\\u2018OnePlus Nord 4\\u2019, \\u2018Realme GT6\\u2019 \\u2013 8 Best Smartphones Of 2024\\n\\n\\n\\nby\\nIram Baig \\n\\nJul 17, 2024\\n\\n\\nin\\nTechnology \\n\\n\\n\\nReading Time: 8 mins read\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\nWe\\u2019re in the middle of 2024 and numerous fascinating and best smartphones are going to be launched. No doubt, smartphones are getting smarter day by day, inch by inch. A person who is going to buy a smartphone will leave no stone unturned in judging the four aspects \\u2014 High-quality camera, Battery life, Storage, Large display and 5G connectivity.\\nSecondly, nowadays many users are looking for features such as water resistance. It\\u2019s crucial to buy the best smartphone as they are now an essential part of our lives. Be it entertainment, communication, or studies, smartphones are becoming a jack of all trades.\\nTechnology is in a state of constant evolution. Foldable smartphones are gaining fame. Brands like Samsung, One Plus, and Pixel are taking the lead in the foldable domain. Let\\u2019s discuss all the latest smartphones of 2024 that are already launched or are expected to be launched soon.\\n\\n\\n\\nRELATED STORIES\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nHow To Properly Care And Store Accessories: The Ultimate Guide\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nHow To Find The Perfect Pair Of Sunglasses\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n8 Best Smartphones Of 2024 \\u2013 Ready To Unleash Beasts?\\n1. OnePlus Nord 4\\n8GB RAM + 256GB Storage | Mercurial Silver | Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b932,999\\n\\nOne Plus Nord 4 is going to be launched on 16 July 2024. It is expected to have a feature of the Snapdragon 7+ Gen 3 processor. The device has an AMOLED display with a 120Hz rate. The rear camera includes a 50 MP primary sensor and an 8 MP ultra-wide camera. The OnePlus Nord 4 can be termed as the best phone under \\u20b930000.\\nFor clicking selfies, a 16MP clear-crisp front camera is given. Moreover, the phone is going to have a whopping 5,500 mAh battery powered by 100W SUPERVOOC fast charging. It will come in three colour options \\u2014 Mercurial Silver, Obsidian Midnight and Oasis Green.\\nPS: The \\u201812GB RAM + 256GB Storage\\u2019 variant is priced at \\u20b935,999 on the official site of OnePlus.\\n2. Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 6\\n12GB RAM + 256GB Storage | Special Edition White | Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b91,64,999\\n\\nThe latest folding phone, Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 6 will be flaunting sharp sides and curved-less corners. It has a triple camera setup with Its primary camera showcasing a sharp 50MP sensor and secondary, a 12MP ultra-wide sensors. The third one will be a 10-megapixel telephoto camera. Additionally, the front camera is going to be a 10MP on-display and a 4MP under display setup. It is expected to come with a 6.3-inch HD+ Dynamic AMOLED screen and a 7.6-inch QXGA+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X Infinity Flex internal foldable screen.\\nIn addition to this, the phone is likely to have a 4,000mAh battery. The phone is going to be launched with the Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 processor. And the good news is that this phone has made a promise of seven years of Android OS and security updates.\\nOther Variants \\u2013 12GB RAM + 512GB Storage\\u00a0at \\u20b91,76,999\\u00a0 || 12GB RAM + 1TB Storage at \\u20b92,00,999\\nColours \\u2013 Crafted Black Special Edition | Silver Shadow | Pink | Navy Blue\\n\\u00a03. Moto G85 5G\\n12GB RAM + 256GB Storage | Urban Grey | Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b919,999\\n\\nMoto G 85 5G is a perfect example of a sleek phone, with a soft touch of vegan leather. It is considered the best 5G phone under \\u20b920000. It has a 16.6 cm display that has deeper blacks. It is launched with the most vibrant colors giving it a distinct style-statement.\\nIts cinematic 10-bit display with DCI-P3 is setting the magic to bring to life. The phone has a built-in storage of 256 GB with. The Moto G85 5G is priced around \\u20b920,000. The handset has a Snapdragon 6s Gen-3 chip for a smooth multi-tasking experience.\\nSecondly, it is supported by a 5,000 mAh battery with 30W charging. Its camera is quite impressive, featuring 50MP + 8MP rear camera powered by shake-free OIS Sony LYTIA 600 and 32MP front camera that allows smooth selfies.\\nOther Variants \\u2013 8GB RAM + 128GB Storage at \\u20b917,999\\nColours \\u2013 Cobalt Blue | Olive Green | Urban Grey\\n4. Oppo Reno12 5G\\n8GB RAM + 256GB Storage | Astro Silver\\u00a0| Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b932,999\\n\\nOppo Reno 12 5G hit the market on 23rd May of this year but the delivery will start from 25th July. The phone comes with a 6.7-inch 120 Hz AMOLED display. Oppo Reno 12 series will come in three unique colours. The camera reveals a 50MP primary Sony IMX890 sensor with OIS, a 5MP auto-focus lens and a 3MP micro lens. The front camera will be equipped with a Oppo-benchmarked 32MP crisp camera. A heavy contender of one of the best 5G smartphone in the segment.\\nThe Reno 12 5G is powered by a 5,000 mAh battery supported by Super Fast SUPERVOOC charger. At the back, the unique design of the Oppo logo in a rectangular shape is given. The experts say, Oppo Reno12 can become a best 5G phone in its rival segment.\\nOther Variants \\u2013 Reno12 Pro 5G | 12GM RAM + 256GB Storage at \\u20b936,999 | 12GM RAM + 512GB Storage at \\u20b940,999\\nColours \\u2013 Sunset Peach | Astro Silver | Matte Brown\\nOppo Reno12 5G Pro Colours \\u2013 Space Brown | Sunset Gold\\n5. Xiaomi CIVI 4 PRO\\n12GB RAM + 512GB Storage | Matcha Green\\u00a0| Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b947,999\\n\\nXiaomi CIVI 4 PRO was launched in India on 21st March 2024. It has a 6.55-inch curved display with a 120 Hz AMOLED screen. The phone is powered by Snapdragon 8s Gen 3 processor. It is flaunting a triple rear camera consisting of 50MP (Main Lens) + 50MP (Telephoto Lens) + 12MP (Ultra-wide Lens), partnered by Leica Optics\\u2019 shake-free feature. The front setup boasts a 32MP + 32MP Dual Selfie AI Camera.\\nXiaomi CIVI 4 PRO has a 4,700 mAh battery that supports 67W turbo charge with ice-loop cooling technology that allows a heat-free performance. Xiaomi CIVI 4 PRO delivers a beast-y experience, justifying the pricing.\\nOther Variants \\u2013 12GB RAM + 512GB Storage at \\u20b942,999\\nColours \\u2013 Shadow Black | Matcha Green | Cruise Blue\\n6. HMD PULSE PRO\\n6GB RAM + 128GB Storage | Glacier Green\\u00a0| Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b915,999\\n\\nThe Nokia phone makers, HMD released their latest budget phone, PULSE PRO in April 2024. The phone\\u2019s features are going to leave you spellbound. It is equipped with a 6.55-inch display flaunting a resolution of 1612\\u00d7720 pixels HD+. Powered by a 5000mAh battery and 20W Fast charging, HMD PULSE PRO, boasts a Unisoc T606 chipset.\\nThe HMD PLUS PRO has dual rear cameras \\u2014 50MP Main + 2MP Depth \\u2014 with a 50MP front camera. The phone has vibrant colour options of Black Ocean, Glacier Green, and Purple. The price is low, at 8,000-9,000.\\n7. Oppo F27 PRO+ 5G\\n8GB RAM + 256GB Storage | Dust Pink\\u00a0| Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b929,999\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nADVERTISEMENT\\n\\nOppo F27 PRO+ 5G, a latest Oppo smartphone, with competitive features has already left an impression in the market. This phone promises a plethora of innovative features that help the users to make up their minds. Shoutout to India\\u2019s first waterproof smartphone with an IP69 rating.\\nOppo F27 PRO+ 5G was launched on 13th June 2024. The phone has a 6.7-inch 120 HZ HD+ AMOLED display. It is powered by a 5000mAh battery supporting 67W SUPERVOOC super fast charging.\\nIt comes with a 64MP primary + 2MP portrait lens, dual rear camera in a circular shape having a silver ring border. With the support of 3D curved AMOLED screen protection, the phone is going to steal your heart.\\nOther Variants \\u2013 8GB RAM + 128GB Storage at \\u20b927,999\\nColours \\u2013 Dust Pink\\u00a0| Midnight Navy\\n8. REALME GT 6\\n16GB RAM + 512GB Storage | Fluid Silver\\u00a0| Priced At \\u2013 \\u20b944,999\\n\\nREALME GT 6 is entering the market on 20th June 2024. It features a 6.78-inch full HD+LTPO AMOLED display with a 120HZ. The phone\\u2019s processor has a Snapdragon 8s Gen 3 chipset.\\u00a0It is powered by a 5,500 MAh battery with support for 120W supercharging.\\nGT 6 is coming with a triple camera setup, having a 50MP Sony primary sensor, 50MP secondary Samsung Lens and 8MP Sony Lens. The front camera is 32MP capable of clicking most sharp and beautiful selfies. REALME GT 6 boasts a Snapdragon 8s Gen 3 Chipset for hassle-free performance.\\nOther Variants \\u2013 8GB RAM + 256GB Storage at \\u20b940,999 | 12GB RAM + 256GB Storage at \\u20b942,999\\nColours \\u2013 Fluid Silver | Razor Green\\nFinal Takeaways\\nThese are some of the best smartphones that are going to launch soon or have already launched. You have to keep an eye out for looking at these smartphones. With the splendid technology advancements roaring in 2024, these smartphones will serve every purpose to you. Get ready to welcome a new era of technology!\\n\\nAlso Checkout \\u2013\\u00a04 Best Tips to Maximise The Life of Your Phone Battery\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nADVERTISEMENT \\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Facebook Twitter Instagram Youtube \\n\\n\\n\\nAbout Us \\nwith our main focus on audience engagement, we deliver out-of-the-box and innovative content so that we stay connected to millions and cater to their interests.\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nADVERTISEMENT \\n\\nCategoriesCategories\\nSelect Category\\nAutomobile\\nBlog\\nBollywood & TV\\nBrand-News\\nBrands\\nBusiness\\nBuying Guides\\nBuzz\\nCareer\\nCelebrity\\nCrypto\\nEntertainment\\nExtras\\nFacts\\nFashion\\nFeatured\\nFinance\\nFood\\nGifts\\nGossip\\nHealth\\nHow To\\nHumour\\nInfotainment\\nLiving\\nMarketing\\nMovie Reviews\\nMy Story\\nOffbeat\\nPartner\\nRelationships\\nScience\\nShopping\\nSports\\nTechnology\\nTips\\nTop 10\\nTravel\\nVideos\\nWorld\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n \\u00a92023 Copyright. RVCJ Digital Media Pvt Ltd\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nNo Result \\n\\n View All Result \\n\\n