performance and aesthetics. I hope the fans like our new Blaze X and enjoy the experiences that it is designed to deliver.\\n\\nLAVA Blaze X: Key Features\\n\\nThe smartphone flaunts a stunning 16.94 cm (6.67\\u201d) 120 Hz Curved AMOLED Display with a punch-hole design providing an immersive experience to the users.\\nPacked with a premium moonstone matte back design with Elegant Deco the new Blaze X exudes style and is a true trendsetter in the category.\\nEquipped with a 64MP + 2MP rear camera featuring the Sony sensor and a 16MP front camera, the new smartphone offers several shooting modes including Dual View Video, Film, Pro Video, Slow Motion, Timelapse, UHD, GIF, Beauty, HDR, Night, Portrait, AI, Pro, Panorama, Filters, Macro, AI Emoji.\\nDelivering an enhanced experience and superlative speed the smartphone brings the latest MediaTek Dimensity 6300 processor with AnTuTu 420K+, paired with three RAM options \\u2013 4GB+4GB*, 6GB+6GB*, and 8GB+8GB* boasting a generous 128GB UFS 2.2 storage to enable smooth multitasking and ample space for storage.\\nBlaze X comes with a 5000mAh battery along Type C port and 33W Fast charging.\\n\\nLava Blaze X price in India\\nThe price of Lava Blaze X in India has been set at Rs. 14,999 for the 4GB RAM + 128GB storage model. The 6GB and 8GB variants with 128GB storage are priced at Rs. 15,999 and Rs. 16,999, respectively.\\nAvailability:\\nThe new Blaze X comes in two stunning color variants Starlight Purple and Titanium Grey. It will be available on Lava e-store and Amazon starting 20th July.\\nContinue Reading \\n\\n\\naffordable smartphoneCurved AMOLED Displaylatest smartphoneLatest smartphones in Indialava blaze xLava International \\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\nYajati Keshari Rout\\n2419 posts\\n0 comments\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n Prev Post\\t\\t\\t\\t\\nNEET-UG paper leak scam: CBI arrests mastermind Rakesh Ranjan\\n\\n\\nNext Post \\nOdisha C&T Dept Inks MoU With Navis HR to Create Overseas Job Opportunity for 